_sText:
This map was created by Toxic! FTW!
xFire: RJOToxic

This is my third map to make. This is a complete recreation of surf_ahooy_b1, which I made completely from scratch. There are 4 different secrets on the map, one giving you full health, another is a secret button for getting out of jail, another is one that gives you a choice between two sniper rifles, and the last you will have to figure out for yourself.  I have to give my main credit to Jacco, for his original creation, surf_ahooy_b1. And to -=Nyko=-A4J & FAJ for helping me test it and critiquing it. I have decompile protected the map.

If you are wanting to create a new version of this map, please add me to your xfire, and have some maps present that you have done to show me you are worthy! :D


Enjoy!

-Toxic



Extract to C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\<username>\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
